  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <article class="prose">
        <p>
          These terms govern your use of <strong>www.comptech-lab.com</strong> ("the site").
          By using the site you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use
          the site.
        </p>
        <p>
          These terms govern access to the site only. Contractual terms for engagements,
          services, deliverables, and any data processing are set out separately in the
          relevant engagement contract.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>use the site in any way that breaches applicable law or regulation;</li>
