          requires prior written permission.
        </p>
        <p>
          Third-party trademarks (Red Hat, OpenShift, NVIDIA, Cisco, HashiCorp, WSO2, AWS,
          Microsoft, Google, and others) referenced on the site remain the property of
          their respective owners and are used here for descriptive purposes only.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Content accuracy &amp; disclaimers</h2>
        <p>
          We make reasonable efforts to keep the site accurate but make no warranty that it
          is complete, current, or error-free. Architectural descriptions, recommendations,
          and engagement durations are illustrative and should not be relied on as advice
          for a specific situation without consultation.
        </p>
        <p>
          The site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied,
          including warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or
          non-infringement.
        </p>

        <h2>4. External links</h2>
